#### Relevant Code Path
```
bool FillableSigningProvider::AddCScript(const CScript& redeemScript)
{
    if (redeemScript.size() > MAX_SCRIPT_ELEMENT_SIZE)
        return error("FillableSigningProvider::AddCScript(): redeemScripts > %i bytes are invalid", MAX_SCRIPT_ELEMENT_SIZE);

    LOCK(cs_KeyStore);
    mapScripts[CScriptID(redeemScript)] = redeemScript;
    return true;
}
```

1. `FillableSigningProvider` is used by `LegacyScriptPubKeyMan`
2. `FlatSigningProvider` is used by `DescriptorScriptPubKeyMan`
